    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm studying for my con law exam and getting stuck on the 2nd amendment stuff. like, is the current supreme court actually following what the founders intended with their interpretation, or is it just a case of judicial overreach? i feel like there's a \"right\" way to read it but textbooks just give both sides. help?",
